Anti-tacrolimus coated microparticles in EDTA buffer with protein stabilizer.
Minimum Concentration: 0.09% solids. Preservatives: sodium azide and ProClin 950.
Conjugate: 1 Bottle (7.8 mL per 100 test bottle/16.0 mL per 500 test bottle)
Tacrolimus acridinium-labeled conjugate in citrate buffer with protein stabilizer.
Minimum Concentration:5.0 ng/mL. Preservative: ProClin 300.
